303619073.name: XY—Furious Fists
303619073.description:
Become King of the Ring!
Trainers, step in the ring and fire up your ferocity for the Pokémon TCG: XY—Furious Fists expansion! Brace yourselves for a grand tournament unlike any before with Mega Lucario-EX and Mega Heracross-EX! And, as the competition intensifies, a host of Pokémon appear for the first time in the Pokémon TCG—each one eager to prove itself as a master of battle! With a team backed by brand-new Trainer cards to power up your Fighting-type Pokémon, your opponents will be left wondering what hit them!

DarkHammerBundle.name: Dark Hammer
DarkHammerBundle.description: Bring the hammer down with the Dark Hammer theme deck! Get your hardest hitters into battle-ready mode quickly with handy Trainer cards like Evosoda and Korrina. Mienshao pulls a tricky hit-and-run as Pangoro hammers away at your opponent's deck. Landorus keeps your team powered up with Energy, and Professor Sycamore refills your hand. With Machamp's Fighting Fury Ability to boost your attacks, your opponent could be in for a dark fate!

EnchantedEchoBundle.name: Enchanted Echo
EnchantedEchoBundle.description: Disrupt your opponent's strategy and protect your team with the Enchanted Echo theme deck! With Sylveon to keep Energy away from opposing Pokémon and Tornadus to shove them back to the Bench, your path will be clear to dish out the hits. Add in the damage prevention of Clefable and Accelgor, plus the healing powers of Victreebel and Potion, and your victory could echo through the ages!
